    "description": "《猎人竞技场：传奇》追求的是RPG、MOBA类的趣味以及对战类高度深奥的战斗心理战。<br>这将完美结合大逃杀模式，带给大家独特而又充满魅力的游戏体验。<br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >融合PvP和PvE趣味的《猎人竞技场：传奇》</h2></strong><br>请体验在逐渐缩小的战场内，杀死怪物、升级技能、获得掉落物品的MOBA与RPG相结合的游戏模式。<br><br>玩家不仅能体验大逃杀模式中最主要的PvP，还可有效运用传统单机动作游戏中的PVE系统，建立起游戏前期及后期的策略。<br><br>《猎人竞技场：传奇》将把重点放在从本质上引人激发竞争的在线模式上，同时为喜欢刺激性PvP的玩家和喜欢相对温和的PvE的玩家们提供舒畅的游戏环境。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/6660ce2ea687aa1534166b66b6e78503.poster.avif?t=1594835846\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/6660ce2ea687aa1534166b66b6e78503.webm?t=1594835846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/6660ce2ea687aa1534166b66b6e78503.mp4?t=1594835846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PvE的核心！攻打副本！但务必时刻警惕后方</h2></strong><br>高风险高收益的副本会提供快速成长和高级装备等丰厚的奖励，但同时也会存在威胁玩家性命的强力的怪物。<br>打败它们，并除掉终极大BOSS即可获得丰厚的奖励，但BOSS的出现会通过系统语音提示给所有人，高收益的诱惑必然会吸引各地的玩家。因此，在PvE过程中被其他玩家偷袭的概率很高也是理所当然的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/227a044fa3651112df0ea3a800998625.poster.avif?t=1594835846\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/227a044fa3651112df0ea3a800998625.webm?t=1594835846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/227a044fa3651112df0ea3a800998625.mp4?t=1594835846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >容易上手的战斗方式，但越是熟练，战斗情境越会深奥</h2></strong><br>刚接触《猎人竞技场：传奇》的新手玩家也能通过简单的按键操作参与激烈战斗。然而，当玩家越来越熟悉游戏，若想取得全面胜利，那就得凭借精良的心理战及战术或策略了。<br>在任何情况下都可以中断技能，因此就算是激烈的速度战，也要预测对方的进攻，有效使用防御和攻击。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/566551ee203201ad40634a0831dc92a4.poster.avif?t=1594835846\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/566551ee203201ad40634a0831dc92a4.webm?t=1594835846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/566551ee203201ad40634a0831dc92a4.mp4?t=1594835846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>攻击敌人使其掉落悬崖或玩家直接进行跳跃攻击等利用地形的战术。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/b29dca2960a3b4a62cc16bb72d281bac.poster.avif?t=1594835846\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/b29dca2960a3b4a62cc16bb72d281bac.webm?t=1594835846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/b29dca2960a3b4a62cc16bb72d281bac.mp4?t=1594835846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>利用近程，中程，远程，支援型等角色们的特性，进行多样的PvP战略<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/66a9052f4450159ba76046f07c730a3f.poster.avif?t=1594835846\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/66a9052f4450159ba76046f07c730a3f.webm?t=1594835846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/66a9052f4450159ba76046f07c730a3f.mp4?t=1594835846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在四面楚歌的战场上，随机缩小的结界将让玩家面临一个又一个的选择点。<br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >决出最后一人的冷酷战场</h2></strong><br>《猎人竞技场：传奇》中玩家的最终目标是在战场上生存到最后。<br>玩家可以根据不同的情况，为了打共同的敌人“怪物BOSS” 可以与其他玩家合作，击退敌人。 为了在战场上生存下去，可能也要成为一个无情的背叛者。<br><br>请不要忘记，在合作与背叛等这一切都被允许的《猎人竞技场：传奇》战场上，<br>你，必须成为最后存活下来的那一个人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/0424da620079acea08a5a2914551234f.poster.avif?t=1594835846\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/0424da620079acea08a5a2914551234f.webm?t=1594835846\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1139700/extras/0424da620079acea08a5a2914551234f.mp4?t=1594835846\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
